U [[Rwanda]] ni [[igihugu]] cy'imisozi<ref>[[Umusozi]]</ref> igihumbi kigizwe n'inzuzi, [[Amashyamba n'imihindagurukire y'ikirere|amashyamba]], [[Umugezi|imigezi]], ndetse n'ibindi bintu nyaburanga bitatse u [[Rwanda]]. tugiye kurebera hamwe ibigaragara ku musozi muremure uzwi ku izina rya  mont Kigali ( umusozi wa Kigali ) uherereye mu [[Umujyi wa Kigali|mujyi wa Kigali]].<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/88278/video-tembera-umusozi-muremure-muri-kigali-hamwe-na-wilson-tours-88278.html</ref>

== Aho uherereye ==
Umusozi wa Kigali ni umwe mu misozi miremire  iri mu murwa w’u [[Rwanda]], ni umusozi ufite amateka, umusozi witwaga Ruhango ya Bwanacyambwe,  witiriwe [[Kigali]],  umurwa w'u Rwanda. Umusozi wa Kigali ukora ku mirenge  ine; Nyamirambo, Mageragere ,Kigali na Kimisagara  yose yo mu [[Akarere ka Nyarugenge|karere ka Nyarugenge]]. Ku musozi wa Kigali uba ureba ahantu hatandukanye mu gihugu, uba ureba [[umujyi wa Kigali]] wose, ukareba [[Intara y'Iburasirazuba|uburasirazuba]], [[Intara y'amajyepfo|mu majyepfo]] no mu [[Intara y’Amajyaruguru y’u Rwanda|majyaruguru]] by’u [[Rwanda]].

 

